name: shit my mexican family has said - food edition #02
description:
i remember trying to test the nightmare theory by making sure i said my good dreams before breakfast. but they told me that good dreams only came true if you kept them to yourself. 🙄 

growing up at the dinner table it was a big deal when you asked someone to pass the salt. they had to place it in front of you because by handing the salt to someone, you were going to hand negative energy and end up fighting with them.
